ntp (1:4.2.5p200-1nexenta2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Rebuilded on new environment

 -- Igor Kozhukhov <igor.kozhukhov@nexenta.com>  Fri, 3 Jun 2011 15:24:32 +0300

