  * NMU
  * Avoid killing all ntpd processes on fresh installs of ntp-server
    (closes: #312331)

 -- Peter Eisentraut <petere@debian.org>  Tue,  6 Jun 2006 02:27:42 +0200

ntp (1:4.2.0a+stable-8.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * 0-day BSP NMU.
