    - While we're at it, take the easy way out and create a separate package
      for the common server parts (init script, cronjobs, ...)
      . Closes: #146275
  * Documented "ntpd -n".
    - Closes: #94975
  * Ship logcheck ignore files for time adjust messages.
    - Closes: #192434
